quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,7,aur ( daur daraaz ) shehron mein jahan tum Zahmat shaqeh ke baghair poanch nahi satke woh tumahray boojh utha kar le jatay hain. kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar nihayat shafqat wala aur meharban hai
16,8,aur isi ne ghoray aur khachar aur gadhay peda kiye taakay tum un par sawaar ho aur ( woh tumahray liye ) ronaqe o zinat ( bhi hain ) aur woh ( aur cheeze bhi ) peda karta hai jin ki tum ko khabar nahi
16,9,aur seedha rasta to khuda taq ja pohanchana hai. aur baaz raste tirhhe hain ( woh is taq nahi pahunchte ) aur agar woh chahta to tum sab ko seedhay raste par chala deta
16,10,wohi to hai jis ne aasman se pani barsaya jisay tum peetay ho aur is se darakht bhi ( shadaab hotay hain ) jin mein tum apne charpayon ko churatay ho
16,11,isi pani se woh tumahray liye khaiti aur Zaitoon aur khajoor aur angoor ( aur be shumaar darakht ) ugata hai. aur har terhan ke phal ( peda karta hai ) ghhor karne walon ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki barri ) nishani hai
16,12,aur isi ne tumahray liye raat aur din aur Sooraj aur chaand ko kaam mein lagaya. aur isi ke hukum se setaaray bhi kaam mein lagey hue hain. samajhney walon ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki bohat si ) nishanain hain
16,13,aur jo terhan terhan ke rangon ki cheeze is ne zameen mein peda kee ( sab tumahray zair farmaan kar dein ) nasiyaat pakarney walon ke liye is mein nishani hai
16,14,aur wohi to hai jis ne darya ko tumahray ikhtiyar meinkiya taakay is mein se taaza gosht khao aur is se zewar ( moti waghera ) nikalu jisay tum pehantay ho. aur tum dekhte ho ke kashtiyan darya mein pani ko phatri chali jati hain. aur is liye bhi ( darya ko tumahray ikhtiyar meinkiya ) ke tum khuda ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo taakay is ka shukar karo
